      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It drives great and is super comfy inside. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and show you around the car!",
