      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This Graphite Metallic sedan is a standout example of a well-cared-for vehicle that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though under close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper. The alloy wheels are wrapped in a set of premium all-season tires with approximately 80% tread life remaining. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features supple black leather seating; the interior remains remarkably clean, with only slight softening of the leather on the driver's seat bolster. Every feature, from the power sunroof and heated seats to the high-fidelity audio system and navigation, is fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced exclusively with synthetic oil every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts with crisp, seamless precision. There are no warning lights on the dash and no fluid leaks beneath the chassis. It provides a quiet, composed ride that feels as solid as the day it was first driven. This is an honest, reliable vehicle that has many years of service left to offer.",
